==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Alarum
<hw>A*lar"um</hw> <pr>(?; 277)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[OE.
<ets>alarom</ets>, the same word as <ets>alarm</ets>, n.]</ety> <def>See
<er>Alarm</er>.</def> <mark>[Now Poetic]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><note>⟦hand⟧ The variant form <xex>alarum</xex> is now commonly
restricted to an alarm signal or the mechanism to sound an alarm (as in
an alarm clock.)</note>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

